&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;刚&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;刚，安倍晋三表示日本和奥组委达成共识，将推迟原定于2020年夏季举行的东京奥运会。并推迟到2021年举办。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.7348643006263048&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicaOtoek4dPyPaRVGuTMhsKppCiaqY0T9rAdgAN4ND9C1rx7Fvyb7bjekw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;479&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5373015873015873&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicajc8PjNUsdTBHskl6mzRIF1hWFCic25UUIFAibDA5dszKyH32YWPHibUSg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;1260&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages js_insertlocalimg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2835443037974683&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicahj97Qo2G1C0JEmBO50xSNZW3Q1aU11Pzn88TzruWGiczOMQIEKxzO3Q/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;395&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;此前早些时间，资深成员庞德表示东京奥运会会推迟。国际奥委会对此回应称：IOC每位成员都有权解释昨天奥委会做出的决定。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2635983263598327&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;478&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicaUYq45HQx93PllrXCb5vMJIUV4gUI75PiaxSKWnNQa5mtvMn0sq0rmlw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;庞德一直是奥委会最具影响力的成员之一，奥组委的回应基本映证了2020东京奥运会被推迟的决定。&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.37116564417177916&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;652&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicaQDKevwLCdgEvAckyeo82DMBgManwDg3tiaPI2gnEbCog4f7GJibnT4sw/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;对此日本奥组委还没有公告发出&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;据悉，推迟东京奥运会讲给日本带来经济损失超过3.2万亿日元（约合2063亿元人民币）&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.689727463312369&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;477&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCo4bYPe0CH8uclzwOhbmicaQVewLKuM67YjiaSqaKVibyRq6APpk7k1MR1hL09MkRyHTOQjc1Z77YnQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;由于全球新冠肺炎蔓延，东京奥运会能否如期举办一直是全民焦点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;国际奥委会主席托马斯·巴赫曾在3月12日明确表示过：&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;将遵循世界卫生组织的建议，决定是否取消或推迟东京奥运会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCkeZ6WyWMlibcpqS5z1m8nUW2OYbNN8ofBGcuYw14P9ylSEByAz9SLbWtufBKyd0o6ybiav9vsquFA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;440&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;275&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.625&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;440&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCkeZ6WyWMlibcpqS5z1m8nUvVFxtqaCc1MicCMUX6BzyTPgMXoXgAV0zObMATl0xJxwoskPjdwr8cA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;图源：微博&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;而此前尽管日本方面一直宣称东京奥运会将如期举行，但曾有声音传出，如果全球疫情仍未好转，&lt;strong&gt;最现实的选择是延期1到2年。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;3月10日，日奥组委理事高乔治之在接受采访时表示：如果今夏奥运会无法举办，他认为最现实的选择是延期1到2年。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.4991922455573506&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;png&quot; data-w=&quot;619&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RiacFDBX14xCkeZ6WyWMlibcpqS5z1m8nUy4RkjeoWFyAFpLmXhTNOGXnJHRrLoziapXkmyqsFJdHyC84CbRX4hkg/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;高桥治之同时也明确表示，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;如果奥运会停办或采取无观众的方式进行，可能会造成巨大的经济损失。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;而延期不到一年的时间则可能和美国的棒球、橄榄球、欧洲足球等赛事时间相撞。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;此前还有消息称，东京奥组委为消除外界对新冠肺炎疫情影响奥运会如期举办的担忧，而提前透露首场比赛将定于7月22日。届时将展开日本女垒与澳大利亚女垒之间的比赛。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; center=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rich_pages&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCkeZ6WyWMlibcpqS5z1m8nUdgFd2r9tqNibKsJicT48meuN7YAAKOZh4X4tiax0XmE21Wgicb0X03sJ1w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;440&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;237&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.5363636363636364&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;440&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xCkeZ6WyWMlibcpqS5z1m8nUbFyYgcict1ibrqicEibF3g0wNibg7OXoEOAzY6ZyxHLKaDkQrJwDQoNbkHA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;但根据此前日本当地的一项网络投票显示，赞成东京奥运会如期举办的网友只有10.5%，另有18.3%建议延期，而62.4%的网友呼吁直接取消奥运会。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;此外，随着海外各国疫情持续加重，运动员方面也发出声音。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p helvetica=&quot;&quot; neue=&quot;&quot; sc=&quot;&quot; sans=&quot;&quot; gb=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; ui=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot; rgb=&quot;&quot; border-box=&quot;&quot; break-word=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;据加拿大广播公司（CBC News）3月23日报道，加拿大奥委会和残奥委表示，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;如果东京奥运会不推迟举办，加拿大将拒绝派运动员参加。 &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

